814
00:36:21,410 --> 00:36:24,830
I can't keep track of all your sworn enemies!

815
00:36:24,830 --> 00:36:30,830
Now, now, Donald has been a model employee, and an excellent prisoner.

816
00:36:31,250 --> 00:36:32,860
