00:37:30,100 --> 00:37:31,680
(Glomgold cackling)

841
00:37:32,450 --> 00:37:33,220
Take 'em down!

842
00:37:34,350 --> 00:37:34,990
Oj då.

843
00:37:36,750 --> 00:37:38,450
We gotta stop the water!

