00:39:40,170 --> 00:39:42,330
Oh, yeah, those guys.

877
00:39:43,660 --> 00:39:44,750
Huey and Louie!

878
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:48,080
...are doing okay!

879
00:39:48,080 --> 00:39:50,320
(grunting)

880
00:39:51,130 --> 00:39:53,330
